{
    "type": "feat",
    "subject": "Add OS family type setting and matching functionality",
    "body": "This commit introduces the ability to set a desired OS family type and determine if the current OS matches it. The setFamily method allows setting the OS family type, and the eval method checks if the current OS matches the set type. This feature enhances the Os class to provide more flexibility and functionality in determining the operating system family."
