}

{
    "type": "refactor",
    "subject": "Remove unnecessary StringBuffer creation in Translate class",
    "body": "This commit refactors the translate method in the Translate class to remove the creation of a StringBuffer object for each line of the source file. This change does not affect the overall purpose of the method, which is to translate files by replacing placeholders with values from a resource map. The method still translates files and writes the translated files to a destination directory, but the processing of each line of the source file is slightly different. This change might have a minor impact on performance or memory usage."
